variable.name: A1M
variable.comment: The lower detectable limit for A1M is 7.55E+05 pg/mL and the upper detectable limit is 5.41E+08 pg/mL. A1M values below or above these limits were set to the lower or upper detectable limit respectively. Use A1M_I to see what records are below and above these limits. A1M values were set to unknown if A1M_CV was greater than or equal to 34.9 for Offspring (IDTYPE = 1) or 27.6 for Gen 3 (IDTYPE = 3).

variable.name: A1M_CV
variable.comment: A1M_CV values were set to unknown if A1M_CV was greater than or equal to 34.9 for Offspring (IDTYPE = 1) or 27.6 for Gen 3 (IDTYPE = 3).

variable.name: EFEMP1
variable.description: EGF containing fibulin-like extracellular matrix protein 1 (EFEMP1) (sample type: plasma)
variable.comment: The lower detectable limit for EFEMP1 is 1.11E+06 pg/mL and the upper detectable limit is 8.15E+08 pg/mL. EFEMP1 values below or above these limits were set to the lower or upper detectable limit respectively. Use EFEMP1_I to see what records are below and above these limits. EFEMP1 values were set to unknown if EFEMP1_CV was greater than or equal to 33.0 for Offspring (IDTYPE = 1) or 23.6 for Gen 3 (IDTYPE = 3).

variable.name: EFEMP1_CV
variable.description: CV for EGF containing fibulin-like extracellular matrix protein 1 (EFEMP1)
variable.comment: EFEMP1_CV values were set to unknown if EFEMP1_CV was greater than or equal to 33.0 for Offspring (IDTYPE = 1) or 23.6 for Gen 3 (IDTYPE = 3).

variable.name: THBS1
variable.comment: The lower detectable limit for THBS1 is 6.18E+05 pg/mL and the upper detectable limit is 1.54E+08 pg/mL. THBS1 values below or above these limits were set to the lower or upper detectable limit respectively. Use THBS1_I to see what records are below and above these limits. THBS1 values were set to unknown if THBS1_CV was greater than or equal to 55.0 for Offspring (IDTYPE = 1) or 63.7 for Gen 3 (IDTYPE = 3).

variable.name: THBS1_CV
variable.comment: THBS1_CV values were set to unknown if THBS1 values were at the lower or upper limit of detection.

variable.name: IGFBP2
variable.description: Insulin-like growth factor binding protein 2 (IGFBP2) (sample type: plasma)
variable.comment: The lower detectable limit for IGFBP2 is 1.63E+06 pg/mL and the upper detectable limit is 1.12E+09 pg/mL. IGFBP2 values below or above these limits were set to the lower or upper detectable limit respectively. Use IGFBP2_I to see what records are below and above these limits. IGFBP2 values were set to unknown if IGFBP2_CV was greater than or equal to 30.4 for Offspring (IDTYPE = 1) or 27.8 for Gen 3 (IDTYPE = 3).

variable.name: IGFBP2_CV
variable.description: CV for insulin-like growth factor binding protein 2 (IGFBP2)
variable.comment: IGFBP2_CV values were set to unknown if IGFBP2_CV was greater than or equal to 30.4 for Offspring (IDTYPE = 1) or 27.8 for Gen 3 (IDTYPE = 3).
